      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROLLING IN MUD (1) has a strong record this trip with six wins and six placings from 15 starts. Recorded a 4 length win (24.91) in a Grade 5 last time at Maitland. Expected to go close. RITZA LAW (2) has been out of the placings at his last two outings but shapes well for this if he can recapture his flying win a few runs back, getting around Q Lakeside over 457m in 25.22. Top win three back and rates a key player again. GOLDSTAR TYSON (5) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (25.56) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 450m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can make it two on the bounce. SANDAVE ABLAZE (7) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
